      "title": "Chilli–Lime Agar Jelly Bites",
      "shortDescription": "Bright, zingy agar jellies with a gentle chilli kick. A ritual snack with a clear ‘finished’ reward.",
      "servings": 12,
      "yieldText": "12 mini jelly bites",
      "difficulty": "easy",
